# Styling & CSS Rules

## Tailwind CSS Guidelines

### Class Order

```html
<!-- ✅ Correct order: Layout > Spacing > Typography > Visual > Interactive -->
<div
  class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 text-lg font-medium bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-50"
></div>
```

### Responsive Design

```html
<!-- ✅ Use responsive prefixes -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
  <div class="text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg">
    <div class="hidden md:block"></div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Custom Classes

- Use the established custom classes from globals.css
- Don't create new custom classes unless absolutely necessary
- Follow the existing naming patterns

### Established Custom Classes

```css
/* ✅ Use these custom classes */
.gradient-luxury
  .gradient-elegant
  .gradient-soft
  .gradient-hero
  .gradient-button
  .gradient-footer
  .luxury-card
  .logo-font
  .hero-title
  .body-text
  .animate-fade-in-up
  .animate-slide-in
  .animate-shimmer;
```

## Color System

### Primary Colors

```css
/* ✅ Use these color variables */
--soft-black: #2D2D2D
--medium-gray: #6B7280
--light-gray: #F3F4F6
--champagne: #f7f3e9
--cream: #faf8f5
--warm-gray: #f5f4f2
--dark-gray: #2a2a2a
--pearl-white: #f9f7f4
--elegant-gold: #d4af37
--rose-gold: #e8b4a0
```

### Tailwind Color Classes

```html
<!-- ✅ Use these Tailwind classes -->
text-soft-black text-medium-gray bg-champagne bg-cream bg-warm-gray
bg-pearl-white border-champagne
```

### HSL Color System

```css
/* ✅ Use HSL format for theme colors */
--background: 0 0% 100%;
--foreground: 0 0% 10%;
--primary: 0 0% 10%;
--border: 0 0% 90%;
```

## Component Styling Patterns

### Button Components

```html
<!-- ✅ Primary button -->
<button className="px-8 py-4 gradient-button hover:gradient-button text-white">
  <!-- ✅ Secondary button -->
  <button
    variant="outline"
    className="px-8 py-4 border-gray-300 hover:bg-white/50"
  >
    <!-- ✅ Ghost button -->
    <button
      variant="ghost"
      className="text-medium-gray hover:text-soft-black"
    ></button>
  </button>
</button>
```

### Card Components

```html
<!-- ✅ Luxury card -->
<div className="luxury-card p-8 rounded-2xl">
  <!-- ✅ Portfolio item -->
  <div className="gallery-item relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl"></div>
</div>
```

### Navigation

```html
<!-- ✅ Navigation container -->
<nav
  className="fixed top-0 w-full bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-md z-50 border-b border-gray-100"
>
  <!-- ✅ Navigation items -->
  <button
    className="text-medium-gray hover:text-soft-black transition-colors"
  ></button>
</nav>
```

## Typography

### Font Classes

```html
<!-- ✅ Logo font -->
<div className="logo-font text-2xl text-soft-black">
  <!-- ✅ Hero title -->
  <h1 className="hero-title text-4xl md:text-6xl">
    <!-- ✅ Body text -->
    <p className="body-text text-lg"></p>
  </h1>
</div>
```

### Font Sizes

```html
<!-- ✅ Use consistent font sizes -->
text-xs /* 12px - small labels */ text-sm /* 14px - body text */ text-base /*
16px - default */ text-lg /* 18px - larger text */ text-xl /* 20px - headings */
text-2xl /* 24px - large headings */ text-4xl /* 36px - hero text */
```

## Spacing System

### Consistent Spacing

```html
<!-- ✅ Use consistent spacing values -->
p-2 /* 8px */ p-4 /* 16px */ p-6 /* 24px */ p-8 /* 32px */ px-4 /* 16px
horizontal */ py-6 /* 24px vertical */ gap-4 /* 16px gap */ space-y-4 /* 16px
vertical spacing */
```

## Animation & Transitions

### Smooth Transitions

```html
<!-- ✅ Use consistent transition classes -->
transition-colors transition-all transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out
```

### Custom Animations

```html
<!-- ✅ Use established animations -->
<div className="animate-fade-in-up">
  <div className="animate-slide-in">
    <div className="animate-shimmer"></div>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Layout Patterns

### Grid Layouts

```html
<!-- ✅ Portfolio grid -->
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
  <!-- ✅ Feature grid -->
  <div className="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8"></div>
</div>
```

### Flexbox Layouts

```html
<!-- ✅ Navigation -->
<div className="flex items-center justify-between">
  <!-- ✅ Centered content -->
  <div className="flex items-center justify-center">
    <!-- ✅ Stacked items -->
    <div className="flex flex-col space-y-4"></div>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Responsive Design Rules

### Breakpoints

```html
<!-- ✅ Use these breakpoints consistently -->
sm: 640px /* Small devices */ md: 768px /* Medium devices */ lg: 1024px /* Large
devices */ xl: 1280px /* Extra large devices */
```

### Mobile-First Approach

```html
<!-- ✅ Start with mobile, then add larger breakpoints -->
<div className="text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg">
  <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <div className="p-4 md:p-6 lg:p-8"></div>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Accessibility

### Focus States

```html
<!-- ✅ Include focus states -->
<button
  className="focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2"
></button>
```

### Color Contrast

```html
<!-- ✅ Ensure sufficient contrast -->
<button className="bg-soft-black text-white">
  <p className="text-medium-gray"></p>
</button>
```

## Dark Mode Support

### Dark Mode Classes

```html
<!-- ✅ Use dark mode variants -->
<div className="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
  <p className="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
    <button className="border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"></button>
  </p>
</div>
```

## Performance

### CSS Optimization

- Use Tailwind's purge feature
- Minimize custom CSS
- Use utility classes over custom styles
- Optimize critical CSS path

### Image Optimization

```html
<!-- ✅ Use proper image sizing -->
<img className="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
<img className="w-16 h-16 rounded-full object-cover" />
```

## Common Anti-Patterns

### ❌ Don't use inline styles

```html
<!-- ❌ Avoid -->
<div style="background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 20px;">
  <!-- ✅ Use Tailwind classes -->
  <div className="bg-gray-100 p-5"></div>
</div>
```

### ❌ Don't create unnecessary custom classes

```css
/* ❌ Avoid */
.custom-button {
  background: linear-gradient(...);
  padding: 1rem;
}

/* ✅ Use existing classes */
<Button className="gradient-button px-4 py-4">
```

### ❌ Don't break the color system

```html
<!-- ❌ Avoid -->
<div className="bg-red-500 text-blue-600">
  <!-- ✅ Use established colors -->
  <div className="bg-destructive text-primary"></div>
</div>
```

## File Organization

### CSS File Structure

```
src/styles/
├── globals.css          /* Main stylesheet */
└── components/          /* Component-specific styles (if needed) */
```

### Import Order in globals.css

```css
/* 1. Tailwind directives */
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

/* 2. Font imports */
@import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap");

/* 3. CSS custom properties */
:root {
  ...;
}

/* 4. Base styles */
@layer base {
  ...;
}

/* 5. Component styles */
@layer components {
  ...;
}

/* 6. Utility styles */
@layer utilities {
  ...;
}
```
